CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FA bin worker from Shrewsbury who has
OL,8,Fbeen striking for a year as part of
OL,9,Fthe ongoing strikes in Birmingham,
OL,10,Fsays he sometimes has to delay his
OL,11,Fchild maintenance payments because of
OL,12,Fhis reduced pay.
OL,14,FDanny Taylor has been a bin worker for
OL,15,F25 years.
OL,17,FHe wakes up in the early hours every
OL,18,Fday to drive from Shrewsbury to do the
OL,19,Fjob, and more recently, to join the
OL,20,Fpicket lines.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FDespite the early starts, he said he
OL,8,Floves the job.
OL,10,F"I like how active it is. It keeps me
OL,11,Ffit. I also like meeting members of
OL,12,Fthe community," he said.
OL,14,FDanny is also a rep for Unite the
OL,15,Funion, whose members are striking
OL,16,Ffollowing plans by Birmingham City
OL,17,FCouncil to scrap the Waste Recycling
OL,18,Fand Collection Officer role, resulting
OL,19,Fin pay cuts of up to #8,000, according
OL,20,Fto the union.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FHe said the workers are on the picket
OL,8,Fline "to win".
OL,10,F"My members are disappointed that
OL,11,Funder a Labour council our workers
OL,12,Frights are being attacked, and they
OL,13,Fwant to know why. That's why they're
OL,14,Fout on the line," he said.
OL,16,FBut after 12 months without full pay,
OL,17,FDanny said he's been forced to cut
OL,18,Fback significantly: "I have a lot of
OL,19,Fbills, I have child maintenance, which
OL,20,Fis important.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,F"So, it's little things like going out
OL,8,Ffor meals which you have to cut back
OL,9,Fon.
OL,11,F"I have to keep shifting my money
OL,12,Faround just to make ends meet," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FDanny rents a bedroom from a friend
OL,16,Fwho lives on a farm as he tries to
OL,17,Fkeep costs down during the dispute. He
OL,18,Falso helps out with jobs on the farm
OL,19,Fto earn extra money.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FHe spends around #70 a week on fuel,
OL,8,Fbut says rising fuel costs as a result
OL,9,Fof the recent conflict in Iran will
OL,10,Fhave a big impact on him but won't
OL,11,Fstop him joining the picket line.
OL,13,F"I'm still going to commute, no matter
OL,14,Fwhat. Even if I had to sell some stuff
OL,15,Fthat I own to be there, I'd be there.'
OL,17,FIt's clear Danny is not going to give
OL,18,Fup, but he does hope the dispute will
OL,19,Fbe resolved soon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,FSo, what will he be doing when it is
OL,8,Fover? He said: "Probably back driving
OL,9,Fbin wagons."
OL,11,FThe city council has continued to
OL,12,Fdefended its decision to scrap the
OL,13,Fwaste role.
OL,15,F"We are committed to creating a
OL,16,Fmodern, sustainable and consistently
OL,17,Freliable waste collection service.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773256283
OL,3,CBin worker forced to cut back
OL,4,C'significantly' after year of reduced
OL,5,Cpay
OL,7,F"The restructure proposal enables us
OL,8,Fto fulfil our commitment to improving
OL,9,Fthe waste service and comes after
OL,10,Fcareful consideration," it said.
OL,12,F"We are disappointed the strike
OL,13,Fcontinues despite our best efforts to
OL,14,Fresolve it. Unfortunately all our
OL,15,Foffers were rejected by Unite."
OL,17,FFor now, the strike continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
